title: Live coverage: SpaceX to launch 27 Starlink satellites on Falcon 9 flight from California
summary: The mission will feature the most Starlink V2 Mini satellites launched on one mission. Liftoff from pad 4 East at Vandenberg Space Force Base is set for Tuesday, Jan. 21, at 7:24 a.m. PST (10:24 p.m. EST, 1524 UTC).
